#  Basic Calculator 

This is a command-line calculator application written in Java as part of Task 1.  
It allows users to perform basic arithmetic operations along with some extended functions.

##  Features

- Addition (+)
- Subtraction (−)
- Multiplication (×)
- Division (÷)
- Square root (√)
- Power (xʸ)

##  Technologies

- Language: Java (Java 17)
- IDE: IntelliJ IDEA
- Platform: Command Line Interface (CLI)

##  How to Run

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/TASK1---Calculator.git
